%20first%20time.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EJeff%20Bezos'%20rocket%20startup%20is%20raising%20%2410%20billion%20at%20a%20%24130%20billion%20valuation%2C%20an%20email%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECEO%20Dave%20Limp%20said%20the%20investment%20will%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Bclear%20vote%20of%20confidence%26quot%3B%20in%20Blue%20Origin's%20mission.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fblue-origin%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EJeff%20Bezos'%20Blue%20Origin%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20raising%20%2410%20billion%20as%20the%20rocket%20startup%20aims%20to%20catch%20up%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspacex-employees-rich-ipo-blue-origin-workers-equity-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk's%20SpaceX%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20memo%20sent%20to%20employees%20on%20Wednesday%20and%20seen%20by%20Business%20Insider%2C%20Blue%20Origin%20CEO%20Dave%20Limp%20said%20the%20company%20would%20raise%20funds%20at%20a%20%24130%20billion%20valuation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20entering%20a%20period%20where%20opportunities%20in%20space%20are%20expanding%20rapidly%2C%26quot%3B%20Limp%20told%20staff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSecuring%20this%20investment%20will%20be%20a%20clear%20vote%20of%20confidence%20from%20investors%20and%20validates%20the%20ambition%20and%20credibility%20of%20what%20we're%20building%20for%20the%20long%20term%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20marks%20the%20first%20time%20that%20Blue%20Origin%2C%20which%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fblue-origin%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBezos%20founded%20in%202000%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20has%20self-funded%20ever%20since%2C%20has%20tapped%20external%20investors%20for%20funding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225584%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20first%20stage%20of%20Blue%20Origin's%20New%20Glenn%20rocket.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4e9eb5d3b3e45765196ac1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223723%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20first%20stage%20of%20Blue%20Origin's%20New%20Glenn%20rocket.%3Cp%3EManuel%20Mazzanti%2FNurPhoto%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20New%20York%20Times'%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2026%2F07%2F08%2Fbusiness%2Fdealbook%2Fbezos-funding-blue-origin.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDealBook%20earlier%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20raise%20and%20said%20it%20is%20being%20led%20by%20asset%20management%20firm%20Coatue%20Management%20with%20a%20%242%20billion%20contribution%20from%20Bezos.%20Limp's%20memo%20has%20not%20yet%20been%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBlue%20Origin%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20Business%20Insider%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20comes%20as%20Blue%20Origin%20races%20to%20catch%20up%20with%20Musk's%20rocketmaker%2C%20which%20has%20established%20a%20commanding%20lead%20in%20the%20space%20industry.%20SpaceX%20has%20completed%20hundreds%20of%20rocket%20launches%2C%20compared%20with%20a%20handful%20of%20orbital%20tests%20by%20Blue%20Origin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspacex-ipo-what-you-need-to-know-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESpaceX%20raised%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20record-breaking%20%2486%20billion%20when%20it%20went%20public%20last%20month%2C%20surpassing%20a%20%242%20trillion%20valuation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERead%20the%20full%20email%20Limp%20sent%20to%20Blue%20Origin%20employees%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EFolks%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EBy%20now%2C%20many%20of%20you%20have%20seen%20the%20news%20that%20Blue%20Origin%20is%20engaging%20with%20outside%20investors%20and%20looking%20to%20raise%20%2410%20billion%20at%20a%20%24130%20billion%20pre-money%20valuation.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20has%20been%20in%20the%20works%20for%20some%20time%20and%20represents%20confidence%20in%20our%20mission%2C%20our%20strategy%2C%20and%20most%20importantly%2C%20the%20work%20each%20of%20you%20has%20done%20to%20build%20Blue%20into%20the%20company%20it%20is%20today.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EWe%20are%20entering%20a%20period%20where%20opportunities%20in%20space%20are%20expanding%20rapidly.%20Securing%20this%20investment%20will%20be%20a%20clear%20vote%20of%20confidence%20from%20investors%20and%20validates%20the%20ambition%20and%20credibility%20of%20what%20we're%20building%20for%20the%20long%20term.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EWhile%20the%20headlines%20will%20naturally%20focus%20on%20the%20dollars%2C%20I'd%20encourage%20all%20of%20us%20to%20think%20about%20today's%20announcement%20differently.%20A%20valuation%20is%20not%20our%20mission.%20It's%20not%20a%20finish%20line.%20It's%20an%20assessment%20of%20what%20investors%20believe%20we%20can%20do%20together.%20What%20matters%20most%20will%20continue%20to%20be%20determined%20by%20our%20execution%2C%20our%20innovation%2C%20and%20our%20ability%20to%20deliver%20for%20customers.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EWe%20will%20share%20more%20details%20as%20we%20have%20them%20and%20will%20take%20questions%20at%20our%20upcoming%20Town%20Hall%20on%20July%2030th.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EIt's%20Worth%20It%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3E-Dave%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20work%20at%20SpaceX%20or%20Blue%20Origin%20and%20have%20information%20to%20share%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20at%20tcarter.41%20on%20Signal%20or%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Atcarter%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Etcarter%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%20Use%20a%20personal%20email%20address%2C%20a%20nonwork%20WiFi%20network%2C%20and%20a%20nonwork%20device%3B%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsider-guide-to-securely-sh