5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAmerigo%20Vespucci.%3Cp%3ETalia%20Lakritz%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%201962%2C%20the%20USS%20Independence%20aircraft%20carrier%20signaled%20to%20Amerigo%20Vespucci%20that%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bthe%20most%20beautiful%20ship%20in%20the%20world%26quot%3B%20when%20the%20two%20ships%20crossed%20paths%20in%20the%20Mediterranean.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20the%20aircraft%20carrier%20USS%20George%20H.W.%20Bush%20repeated%20the%20compliment%20when%20the%20Italian%20ship%20sailed%20nearby%2C%20conveying%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20are%20still%2C%20after%2060%20years%2C%20the%20most%20beautiful%20ship%20in%20the%20world.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAside%20from%20World%20War%20II%2C%20Amerigo%20Vespucci%20has%20been%20continuously%20active%20since%201931.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Aboard%20Amerigo%20Vespucci.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4d1940965805a2c542d988%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAboard%20Amerigo%20Vespucci.%3Cp%3ETalia%20Lakritz%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMeasuring%20329%20feet%20long%20with%2030%2C400%20square%20feet%20of%20sail%2C%20Amerigo%20Vespucci%20carries%2016%20officers%2C%2070%20non-commissioned%20officers%2C%20190%20sailors%2C%20and%2C%20in%20the%20summertime%2C%20130%20cadets%20from%20the%20Italian%20Naval%20Academy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20ingathering%20of%20historic%20ships%20from%20around%20the%20world%20offered%20a%20fitting%20tribute%20on%20America's%20250th%20birthday.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ships%20at%20Sail4th%20250.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4e76e5d3a449ec3445f4d1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EShips%20at%20Sail4th%20250.%3Cp%3ETalia%20Lakritz%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20largest%20maritime%20gathering%20in%20US%20history%20offered%20an%20impressive%20display%20of%20ships%20and%20modern%20naval%20alliances.%20What%20surprised%20me%2C%20though%2C%20were%20the%20personal%20connections.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20active-duty%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fww2-museum-ships-submarines-iran-war-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUS%20Navy%20ships%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20older%20veterans%20regaled%20crew%20members%20with%20tales%20from%20their%20time%20at%20sea%2C%20comparing%20the%20advancements%20in%20technology%20and%20the%20patches%20on%20their%20uniforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20foreign%20ships%2C%20visitors%20chatted%20excitedly%20with%20uniformed%20crew%20members%20in%20their%20native%20languages%20%E2%80%94%20Spanish%2C%20Polish%2C%20Swedish%2C%20Italian%20%E2%80%94%20either%20as%20native%20speakers%20themselves%20or%20in%20broken%20sentences%20as%20they%20attempted%20to%20practice%20their%20skills.%20A%20crew%20member%20on%20Uruguay's%20Capitan%20Miranda%20told%20me%20that%20ships%20serve%20as%20%26quot%3Bfloating%20embassies%2C%26quot%3B%20promoting%20international%20relations%20while%20also%20providing%20a%20taste%20of%20home%20to%20citizens%20and%20expats%20abroad.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoarding%20ships%20from%20Poland%20and%20the%20Dominican%20Republic%2C%20two%20countries%20included%20in%20my%20own%20family's%20history%20as%20American%20immigrants%2C%20also%20held%20special%20significance%20for%20me.%20I%20sent%20a%20steady%20stream%20of%20photos%20to%20the%20family%20group%20chat%2C%20marveling%20at%20seeing%20parts%20of%20our%20journey%20to%20America%20represented%20by%20the%20towering%20sails.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20definitely%20one%20of%20the%20best%20birthday%20parties%20I've%20been%20to%20in%20a%20while.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerica-250-ship-tours-us-navy-2026-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1783538998000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4e97f5d3a449ec3445f5f7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerica-250-ship-tours-us-navy-2026-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20celebration%20of%20America's%20milestone%20250th%20birthday%2C%20New%20York%20City%20hosted%20a%20historic%20display%20of%20military%20partnerships%20and%20naval%20tradition.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tlakritz%40businessinsider.com%20(Talia%20Lakritz)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Computer%20scientist%20who%20created%20world's%20first%20chatbot%20in%20the%201960s%20spent%20his%20whole%20life%20warning%20that%20AI%20should%20never%20replace%20humans%2C%20and%20the%20reason%20will%20shock%20you%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1783538978000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-132271966%2Cimgsize-92454.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Fcomputer-scientist-who-created-worlds-first-chatbot-in-the-1960s-spent-his-whole-life-warning-that-ai-should-never-replace-humans-and-the-reason-will-shock-you%2Farticleshow%2F132271918.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F132271918.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EIn%20the%201960s%2C%20Joseph%20Weizenbaum%20pioneered%20the%20first%20chatbot%2C%20named%20Eliza%2C%20which%20unveiled%20a%20startling%20truth%3A%20humans%20could%20emotionally%20bond%20with%20machines.%20This%20insight%20led%20him%20to%20caution%20against%20the%20potential%20of%20AI%20usurping%20human%20empathy.%20Weizenbaum's%20assertions%20about%20the%20risks%20of%20deceiving%20machines%20fostering%20misplaced%20trust%