A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Clayton%20Davis%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20To%20Remove%20Syria%20From%20Terror%20Blacklist%20In%20Move%20To%20Boost%20Ties%20With%20Al-Sharaa%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22The%20United%20States%20said%20Wednesday%20it%20will%20delist%20Syria%20as%20a%20state%20sponsor%20of%20terrorism%2C%20a%20decades-old%20designation%20that%20severely%20impeded%20investment%2C%20in%20a%20new%20vote%20of%20confidence%20in%20leader%20Ahmed%20al-Sharaa.%22%2C%22published%22%3A1783538939000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-to-remove-syria-from-terror-blacklist-in-move-to-boost-ties-with-al-sharaa-11746316%23publisher%3Dnewsstand%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20United%20States%20said%20Wednesday%20it%20will%20delist%20Syria%20as%20a%20state%20sponsor%20of%20terrorism%2C%20a%20decades-old%20designation%20that%20severely%20impeded%20investment%2C%20in%20a%20new%20vote%20of%20confidence%20in%20leader%20Ahmed%20al-Sharaa.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-to-remove-syria-from-terror-blacklist-in-move-to-boost-ties-with-al-sharaa-11746316%23publisher%3Dnewsstand%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-to-remove-syria-from-terror-blacklist-in-move-to-boost-ties-with-al-sharaa-11746316%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-to-remove-syria-from-terror-blacklist-in-move-to-boost-ties-with-al-sharaa-11746316%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Facebook%20users%20keep%20accidentally%20posting%20onto%20Threads%20%E2%80%94%20and%20Threads%20users%20love%20it.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226720%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Senior%20man%20using%20laptop%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4eaadcd3a449ec3445f6d3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224480%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMark%20Zuckerberg's%20Meta%20started%20Threads%20three%20years%20ago.%20It%20now%20says%20it's%20up%20to%20500%20million%20monthly%20active%20users.%20I%20wonder%20how%20many%20people%20actually%20know%20they're%20posting%20there.%3Cp%3EBasak%20Gurbuz%20Derman%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmetas-threads-exec-said-its-expanding-messaging-for-power-users-2026-5%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMeta's%20Threads%3C%2Fa%3E%20says%20it%20has%20500%20million%20monthly%20active%20users.%20A%20lot%20of%20those%20people%20are%20cross-posting%20from%20Facebook%20or%20Instagram.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESome%20of%20those%20cross-posters%20don't%20seem%20to%20realize%20they're%20doing%20it.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOne%20classic%20%E2%80%94%20and%20sad%20%E2%80%94%20example%20is%20a%20woman%20posting%20about%20her%20husband's%20death.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20there%20is%20one%20standout%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-threads-dear-algo-gives-users-control-over-their-feeds-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EThreads%3C%2Fa%3E%20meme%2C%20it's%3A%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20Richard's%20wife.%20He%20has%20passed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20a%20joke%20from%20some%20clever%20user%3B%20it%20was%20a%20real%2C%20grieving%20widow%20who%20apparently%20logged%20onto%20her%20husband's%20account%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eback%20in%20December%20to%20announce%20that%20he'd%20died.%20Somehow%2C%20the%20post%20got%20picked%20up%20by%20the%20Threads%20algorithm%2C%20which%20showed%20it%20to%20thousands%20of%20strangers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20Wednesday%2C%20it%20had%2018%2C000%20likes%20and%201%2C800%20comments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E(I%20reached%20out%20to%20Richard's%20wife%2C%20but%20didn't%20hear%20back.%20I%20wish%20her%20the%20best.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2262c92961-2d23-4bfe-8caf-305b6ba587ab%5C%22%3ECross-posts%20from%20Instagram%20and%20Facebook%20are%20all%20over%20Threads%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThreads%20%E2%80%94%20Meta's%20answer%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fx-meta-employee-snack-offerings-talent-wars-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EX%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20just%20celebrated%20its%20third%20anniversary.%20It's%20slowly%20but%20surely%20built%20up%20a%20large%20user%20base.%20Meta%20says%20it%20has%20more%20than%20500%20million%20monthly%20active%20users%20%E2%80%94%20more%20than%20X.%20That%20count%20is%20certainly%20helped%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-internal-deck-for-threads-shows-strategy-for-the-platform-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EThreads'%20cross-promotion%20on%20Instagram%20and%20Facebook%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Threads%20posts%20often%20appear%20in%20the%20Instagram%20app%2C%20encouraging%20people%20to%20click%20into%20them%20and%20download%20or%20open%20the%20separate%20Threads%20app.%20(Meta%20has%20said%20the%20percentage%20of%20daily%20active%20users%20who%20open%20the%20app%20directly%20instead%20of%20tapping%20into%20it%20from%20Instagram%20has%20grown%20over%20time%2C%20although%20they%20declined%20to%20share%20numbers.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAggressively%20cross-promoting%20from%20Instagram%20and%20Facebook%20is%20a%20great%20user-acquisition%20technique.%20But%20there's%20another%20side%20of%20the%20coin%20that%20has%20created%20a%20strange%20culture%20on%20Threads%3A%20the%20feeling%20that%20half%20the%20people%20posting%20there%20don't%20even%20know%20what%20app%20they're%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20option%20to%20cross-post%20from%20Facebook%20or%20Instagram%20is%20not%20turned%20on%20by%20default%2C%20and%20on%20Instagram%2C%20the%20option%20is%20buried%20a%20little%20deep%20in%20the%20settings.%20However%2C%20on%20Facebook%2C%20when%20you%20create%20a%20new%20post%20in%20the%20mobile%20app%2C%20the%20option%20to%20cross-post%20to%20Threads%20is%20a%20simple%20%26quot%3BOn%26quot%3B%20tap%20of%20the%20Threads%20%40%20logo%20right%20at%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20post.%20Once%20you%20tap%20it%20%26quot%3BOn%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20stays%20on%20for%20subsequent%20posts.%20(You%20can%20always%20turn%20it%20off.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJocelyn%20Ramsey%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20Meta%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20it%20has%20recently%20added%20more%20friction%20to%20stop%20people%20from%20accidentally%20cross-posting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221290%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22screenshot%20of%20the%20facebook%20post%20compose%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4ea3bad3b3e45765196b07%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22645%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWhen%20posting%20to%20Facebook%2C%20you%20can%20turn%20Threads%20cross-posting%20%26quot%3BOn%26quot%3B%20with%20a%20single%20tap.%3Cp%3Escreenshot%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20unclear%20how%20much%20Threads%20content%20is%20cross-posted%3B%20Meta%20doesn't%20say.%20In%20my%20experience%2C%20the%20vast%20majority%20of%20posts%20I%20see%20on%20Threads%20are%20from%20engaged%20users%20who%20know%20where%20they%20are%20and%20are%20generally%20enjoying%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20if%20I%20scroll%20a%20little%2C%20I%20almost%20always%20see%20at%20least%20a%20few%20posts%20that%20seem%20to%20be%20from%20someone%20who%20doesn't%20realize%20they're%20cross-posting%20to%20Threads.%20There%20are%20little%20tells%20like%20mentioning%20family%20members%20by%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20Threads'%20algorithm%20is%20so%20personalized%2C%20it's%20possible%20I%20see%20these%20unintended%20cross-posts%20more%20than%20other%20people.%20(I%20do%20tend%20to%20lurk%20around%20on%20there%20a%20lot.)%20But%20I%20can%20tell%20from%20engagement%20numbers%20that%20sometimes%20these%20clueless%20cross-posts%20go%20viral%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20not%20just%20me%20seeing%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccidental%20posts%20have%20become%20part%20of%20the%20fabric%20of%20Threads%20culture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221257%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20screenshot%20on%20Threads%2C%20where%20people%20seem%20to%20be%20accidentally%20cross-posting.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4d22705dc133dbf310da6c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221237%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThis%20post%20that%20came%20up%20in%20my%20Threads%20feed%20seems%20to%20be%20from%20a%20man%20who%20thinks%20he's%20direct%20messaging%20someone%20else%3B%20instead%2C%20it%20got%20picked%20up%20by%20the%20Threads%20algorithm%20and%20shown%20to%20me.%3Cp%3EThreads%20screengrab%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226d0b6095-47a5-4af0-a2b2-d60af5212e66%5C%22%3EThe%20'gas%20leak'%20social%20network%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELess%20than%20a%20year%20after%20it%20launched%2C%20Max%20Read%20called%20Threads%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmaxread.substack.com%2Fp%2Fthreads-is-the-gas-leak-social-network%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bgas-leak%20social%20network%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20because%2C%20as%20he%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BEveryone%20on%20the%20platform%2C%20including%20you%2C%20seems%20to%20be%20suffering%20some%20kind%20of%20minor%20brain%20damage.%26quot%3B%20At%20the%20time%2C%20the%20issue%20wasn't%20Instagram%20or%20Facebook%20cross-posting%20(which%20wasn't%20yet%20enabled)%3B%20it%20was%20that%20the%20kinds%20of%20people%20who%20gravitated%20to%20Threads%20often%20weren't%20hardened%20capital-P%C2%A0%3Cem%3EPosters%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20those%C2%A0used%20to%20the%20fast%20pace%20and%20edge%20of%20old%20Twitter%20and%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20people%20posting%20on%20Threads%20seemed%20like%20innocent%20babes%2C%20incapable%20of%20identifying%20sarcasm%20or%20%3Cem%3Eshitposts.%3C%2Fem%3E%20(I%20found%20it%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthreads-meta-engagement-rage-bait-viral-katie-notopoulos-i-tried-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%20incredibly%20easy%20to%20ragebait%20on%20Threads%3C%2Fa%3E.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20now%20it's%20not%20so%20much%20the%20%3Cem%3Egas%20leak%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20the%20%3Cem%3Eplatform%20leak%3C%2Fem%3E.%20It's%20the%20people%20%E2%80%94%20typically%20older%20people%20who%20are%20less%20used%20to%20social%20media%20%E2%80%94%20who%20flipped%20on%20the%20toggle%20to%20crosspost%20and%20never%20check%20the%20Threads%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20take%20for%20granted%20that%20text-mased%20social%20networks%20have%20all%20sorts%20of%20unspoken%20rules%3A%20Don't%20post%20your%20address.%20Don't%20post%20your%20phone%20number.%20Don't%20post%20photos%20of%20your%20grandkids%20or%20of%20kids%20not%20fully%20clothed.%20That%20celebrity%20asking%20you%20for%20a%20gift%20card%20is%20probably%20not%20really%20the%20celebrity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20isn't%20really%20a%20problem%20on%20something%20like%20Bluesky%20or%20even%20on%20X%2C%20which%20typically%20has%20more%20experienced%20users.%20But%20Threads%20has%20so%20many%20Facebook%20and%20Instagram%20users%20%E2%80%94%20people%20with%20less%20experience%20navigating%20the%20choppy%20waters%20of%20algorithmic%20text-based%20social%20platforms.%20This%20creates%20a%20situation%20where%20there%20are%20Haves%20who%20understand%20social%20platform%20dynamics%20and%20Have-nots%20who%20don't.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20one%20of%20the%20dominant%20forms%20of%20entertainment%20on%20Threads%20is%20to%20chuckle%20at%20the%20Have-nots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20someone%20who%20understands%20how%20Threads%20works%2C%20I%20admit%20I've%20enjoyed%20the%20people-watching%20aspect%20of%20seeing%20the%20platform%20leak.%20But%20I%20have%20to%20imagine%20this%20is%20a%20terrible%20experience%20for%20the%20people%20caught%20in%20the%20crosshairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthreads-richard-has-passed-instagram-cross-posting-facebook-instagram-2026-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1783538895000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4eaaecd3a449ec3445f6d4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthreads-richard-has-passed-instagram-cross-posting-facebook-instagram-2026-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Threads%20is%20full%20of%20people%20who%20seem%20to%20be%20accidentally%20crossposting%20from%20Instagram%20or%20Facebook%2C%20like%20the%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20Richard's%20wife%26quot%3B%20woman.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22knotopoulos%40businessinsider.com%20(Katie%20Notopoulos)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A97%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Justin%20Bieber%20Joins%20Madonna%2C%20BTS%20and%20Shakira%20for%20FIFA%20World%20Cup%20Final%20Halftime%20Show%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1783538184000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236804858%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Justin%20Bieber%20has%20been%20added%20as%20a%20performer%20to%20the%20FIFA%20World%20Cup%20Final%20Halftime%20Show%2C%20joining%20the%20lineup%20as%20a%20co-headliner%20alongside%20Madonna%2C%20Shakira%20and%20BTS.%20FIFA%20and%20Global%20Citizen%20are%20staging%20the%20first%20Halftime%20Show%20in%20FIFA%20World%20Cup%20history%20on%20July%2019%20at%20New%20York%20New%20Jersey%20Stadium.%20The%2011-minute%20spectacle%20will%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Steven%20J.%20Horowitz%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Amazon%20MGM%20Studios%20Ups%20Kara%20Smith%20to%20Head%20of%20Drama%20TV%20as%20Jen%20Chambers%2C%20Michael%20McDonald%20and%20Odetta%20Watkins%20Exit%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1783538096000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2