ss%20me.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWalmart%20had%20the%20lowest%20prices%2C%20and%20Kroger%20was%20close%20behind%20%E2%80%94%20but%20I%20may%20have%20gotten%20lucky.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-walmart-lower-prices-white-house-request-2026-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EWalmart%20announced%20rollbacks%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20more%20than%20250%20items%2C%20my%20ears%20naturally%20perked%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20chain%20shared%20the%20featured%20price%20drops%20in%20a%20press%20release%20on%20Monday%2C%20highlighting%20a%20few%20of%20the%20specific%20products%20that%20will%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmore-americans-are-ditching-summer-vacations-while-others-spend-more-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elower%20prices%20for%20summer%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Truth%20Social%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcommodities%2Foil-wti-brent-crude-price-us-iran-war-trump-ceasefire-2026-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump%3C%2Fa%3E%20credited%20the%20price%20reductions%20to%20his%20administration's%20%26quot%3Brequest%20to%20celebrate%20our%20great%20Country's%20250th%20birthday%26quot%3B.%20Walmart%20didn't%20mention%20the%20White%20House%20or%20the%20celebration%20as%20motives%20in%20its%20press%20release%20and%20has%20declined%20to%20comment%20on%20whether%20the%20sales%20resulted%20from%20a%20meeting%20with%20the%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20matter%20how%20these%20savings%20came%20about%2C%20I%20was%20just%20happy%20to%20see%20them.%20Walmart's%20known%20for%20having%20low%20prices%2C%20and%20I%20was%20curious%20how%20its%20newly%20reduced%20ones%20would%20compare%20with%20other%20major%20grocers'.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20I%20wrote%20down%20the%20specific%20items%20mentioned%20in%20the%20price-drop%20announcement%20and%20headed%20to%20Walmart%20and%20two%20of%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwalmart-grocery-sales-us-compared-kroger-albertsons-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebiggest%20competitors%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20Kroger%20and%20Amazon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20how%20the%20prices%20measured%20up%20as%20I%20shopped%20the%20same%20list%20at%20each%20retailer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EGround%20beef%20prices%20were%20basically%20the%20same%20across%20the%20board.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Side%20by%20side%20of%20ground%20beef%20at%20Walmart%20for%20%244.94%20a%20pound%20and%20ground%20beef%20at%20Kroger%20for%20%245.99%20a%20pound%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4e5c6694175b76817201df%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESavannah%20Born%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWalmart's%20press%20release%20specifically%20mentions%20a%20rollback%20on%20the%201-pound%20roll%20of%2073%25%20ground%20beef%2C%20so%20that's%20what%20I%20selected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20promised%2C%20Walmart's%20beef%2C%20originally%20%246.94%2C%20came%20to%20%245.94%20for%20a%201-pound%20roll.%20Kroger's%20was%20very%20close%20behind%20at%20%245.99.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20couldn't%20find%20any%201-pound%20packages%20of%2073%25%20lean%20ground%20beef%20on%20Amazon%2C%20only%20a%20bulky%203-pound%20roll.%20It%20worked%20out%20to%20%246.15%20per%20pound.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWalmart's%20price%20was%20the%20lowest%2C%20but%20I%20wasn't%20particularly%20impressed%20by%20any%20of%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWalmart%20had%20the%20sweetest%20corn%20prices.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Box%20of%20corn%20at%20Walmart%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4e5cfa94175b76817201ef%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESavannah%20Born%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20can't%20comment%20on%20the%20actual%20sweetness%20in%20terms%20of%20taste%2C%20but%20Walmart's%20sweet%20corn%20was%20a%20bargain.%20It%20cost%20just%20%240.25%20per%20ear%2C%20compared%20to%20%240.40%20per%20ear%20at%20Kroger%20and%20a%20whopping%20%241.25%20per%20ear%20on%20Amazon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20added%20four%20ears%20to%20my%20cart%20at%20each%20retailer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ENeither%20Amazon%20nor%20Kroger%20could%20compete%20with%20Walmart%20on%20cherries.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Composite%20of%20cherry%20prices%20at%20Walmart%2C%20Kroger%2C%20and%20Amazon%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4e5ebed3b3e4576519685a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESavannah%20Born%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Walmart%20press%20release%20specifically%20mentioned%202.2-pound%20bags%20of%20fresh%20red%20cherries%20would%20be%20reduced%20from%20%2411.18%20to%20%245.63.%20My%20local%20store%20only%20carried%201-pound%20bags%2C%20but%20they%20also%20came%20to%20%242.50%20per%20pound%20like%20the%20ones%20mentioned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKroger's%20red%20cherries%20were%20on%20sale%2C%20discounted%20from%20%244.49%20to%20%242.99%20per%20pound.%20Amazon%20tied%20with%20Kroger%20at%20%242.99%20per%20pound.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20worth%20noting%20that%20Kroger%20deals%20like%20these%20are%20only%20valid%20with%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-people-love-kroger-2015-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EKroger%20Plus%20Card%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20which%20I%20have%2C%20since%20it's%20a%20free%20loyalty%20card.%20Without%20it%2C%20they'd%20have%20cost%20me%20the%20full%20%244.49.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20also%20surprised%20to%20find%20such%20a%20great%20sale%20in%20the%20store%20since%20I%20hadn't%20seen%20it%20mentioned%20in%20Kroger's%20weekly%20flyer.%20I%20wondered%20if%20it%20may%20have%20been%20a%20more%20last-minute%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fiamazon-fix-groceries-beat-walmart-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ediscount%20to%20compete%20with%20Walmart%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20the%20Monday%20announcement.%20%3Cem%3EKroger%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20Business%20Insider's%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ETo%20my%20delight%2C%20all%20three%20retailers%20had%20generic%2048-ounce%20tubs%20of%20ice%20cream%20for%20under%20%243.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%2248-ounce%20tubs%20of%20Kroger%20ice%20cream%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4e6061d3a449ec3445f3d4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESavannah%20Born%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWalmart%20highlighted%2048-ounce%20tubs%20of%20its%20store-brand%20Great%20Value%20ice%20cream%20being%20reduced%20from%20%242.97%20to%20%242.50.%20That's%20exactly%20what%20I%20found%20in%20the%20store.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%20had%20the%20same-sized%20tubs%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-fresh-stores-closing-focusing-on-whole-foods-delivery-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAmazon%20Grocery%3C%2Fa%3E%20ice%20cream%20available%20for%20%242.97%2C%20the%20price%20Walmart's%20was%20before%20the%20cut.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKroger%20had%20the%20cheapest%2048-ounce%20tubs%20on%20sale%20for%20%241.99%20%E2%80%94%20marked%20down%20from%20%242.99.%20With%20prices%20this%20good%2C%20I%20would%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-vanilla-ice-cream-store-brand-review-ranking-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehappily%20bought%20ice%20cream%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20all%20three%20retailers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAn%208-ounce%20bag%20of%20Lay's%20classic%20potato%20chips%20felt%20like%20a%20steal%20at%20Kroger%2C%20but%20the%20deal's%20already%20gone.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lay's%20classic%20potato%20chips%20at%20Kroger%20%20for%20%243.99%20%20on%20sale%20for%20%243.29%20with%20weekly%20digitaldeal%20for%20%241.99%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4e6228d3a449ec3445f3de%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESavannah%20Born%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAn%208-ounce%20bag%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftaste-test-lays-classic-potato-chips-every-flavor-ranked%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ELay's%20classic%20potato%20chips%3C%2Fa%3E%20cost%20%242.50%20at%20Walmart%2C%20marked%20down%20from%20%242.97.%20The%20same%20bag%20of%20chips%20was%20also%20%242.50%20on%20Amazon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20Kroger%2C%20these%20chips%20had%20several%20prices%20in%20front%20of%20it.%20The%208-ounce%20bag%20was%20originally%20priced%20at%20%243.99%2C%20listed%20at%20%243.29%20with%20card%2C%20and%20then%20labeled%20%241.99%20with%20card%20%3Cem%3Eand%3C%2Fem%3E%20a%20clipped%20digital%20coupon%20as%20part%20of%20a%20weekly%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKroger's%20price%20was%20the%20best%2C%20but%20I%20only%20just%20caught%20this%20deal%2C%20which%20expired%20July%207.%20(Kroger's%20digital%20deals%20refresh%20every%20Wednesday%2C%20and%20I%20visited%20Kroger%20on%20a%20Tuesday.)%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%20of%20writing%2C%20the%20deal%20is%20already%20gone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EFrito-Lay%20Family%20Fun%20boxes%20were%20comparable%20at%20Kroger%20and%20Walmart%2C%20but%20I%20didn't%20find%20the%20same%20deal%20on%20Amazon.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Side%20by%20side%20of%20Family%20Fun%20pack%20at%20Walmart%20next%20to%20same%20pack%20on%20display%20at%20Kroger%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4e9ae9b3a8c16f7e8ec8da%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAt%20Walmart%20(left)%20and%20Kroger%20(right)%2C%20I%20could%20get%20a%20Frito-Lay%20Family%20Fun%20variety%20pack%20for%20under%20%2410.%3Cp%3ESavannah%20Born%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWalmart%20reduced%20the%20price%20of%20the%20Frito-Lay%20Family%20Fun%2018-bag%20variety%20pack%20including%20a%20mix%20of%20Cheetos%2C%20Fritos%2C%20Funyuns%2C%20Lay's%2C%20and%20Ruffles%20from%20%249.97%20to%20%248.97.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKroger%20originally%20listed%20the%20variety%20packs%20at%20%2410.99%2C%20but%20price-drop%20stickers%20now%20had%20them%20marked%20%249.99.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Amazon%2C%20this%20pack%20was%20available%20for%20%249.99%20through%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-amazon-fresh-struggled-to-break-through-workers-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAmazon%20Fresh%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20I%20didn't%20use%20because%20I'm%20already%20a%20Prime%20member%20and%20wasn't%20ordering%20enough%20to%20hit%20the%20minimum%20spend%20and%20avoid%20a%20delivery%20fee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20other%20option%20was%20to%20order%20this%20pack%20through%20a%20low-rated%20third-party%20seller%20for%20a%20whopping%20%2421.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWalmart%20and%20Amazon%20had%20great%20prices%20on%20disposable%20plates.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Pack%20of%20plates%20at%20Walmart%20for%20%248.97%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4e753ad3a449ec3445f4c8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESavannah%20Born%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWalmart's%20release%20highlighted%20a%20200-pack%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwalmart-frozen-meals-great-value-bettergoods-review-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGreat%20Value%3C%2Fa%3E%20disposable%20plates%20being%20marked%20down%20from%20%249.97%20to%20%248.97%2C%20or%20%240.04%20per%20plate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Amazon%2C%20the%20same%20quantity%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-amazonbasics-private-label-brands-7-22%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAmazon%20Basics%3C%2Fa%3E%20plates%20was%20%2410.60%2C%20or%20%240.05%20per%20plate.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20local%20Kroger%20didn't%20have%20any%20200-packs%2C%20and%20the%20closest%20I%20found%20was%20150%20plates%20for%20%249.99.%20They%20worked%20out%20to%20%240.07%20per%20plate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20I%20ever%20need%20such%20a%20large%20quantity%20of%20disposable%20plates%2C%20I'm%20totally%20turning%20to%20Walmart%20or%20Amazon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20got%20lucky%20with%20Coca-Cola%20and%20Pepsi%20deals%20at%20Kroger.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Soda%20aisle%20at%20Kroger%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4e67b1d3b3e457651968c0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESavannah%20Born%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWalmart%20marked%20down%20select%2024-packs%20of%20sodas%2C%20including%20Coca-Cola%20and%20Diet%20Pepsi.%20With%20the%20rollback%20prices%2C%20they%20worked%20out%20to%20%240.42%20per%20can.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20local%20Kroger%20didn't%20have%20any%2024-packs%20of%20these%20drinks%2C%20so%2012-packs%20were%20the%20next%20best%20option.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKroger's%20a%2012-pack%20of%20Coca-Cola%20or%20Pepsi%20cans%20typically%20costs%20%2411.99%2C%20or%20%241%20per%20can.%20However%2C%20when%20I%20visited%2C%20the%20store%20was%20running%20a%20%26quot%3Bbuy%20two%2C%20get%20three%20free%26quot%3B%20deal%2C%20which%20meant%20I%20could%20get%2060%20cans%20for%20the%20price%20of%2024.%20It%20brought%20the%20price%20per%20can%20down%20to%20%240.40.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%20didn't%20have%20any%2024-packs%20readily%20available%20to%20me%2C%20either.%20I%20could%20buy%2012-packs%2C%20though%2C%20so%20I%20grabbed%20two%20of%20each.%20On%20Amazon%2C%20my%20Coca-Cola%20came%20to%20%240.70%20per%20can%2C%20whereas%20Diet%20Pepsi%20was%20%240.66%20per%20can.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EShopping%20at%20Kroger%20felt%20like%20a%20gamble%20%E2%80%94%20and%20Amazon's%20prices%20seemed%20to%20be%20all%20over%20the%20place.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224896%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Woman%20smiling%20with%20shopping%20cart%20in%20Kroger%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4e82a3d3a449ec3445f543%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223672%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESavannah%20Born%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20Walmart%2C%20where%20rollbacks%20tend%20to%20last%20several%20weeks%20and%20are%20available%20to%20any%20shopper%2C%20many%20of%20Kroger's%20sale%20prices%20only%20last%20for%20seven%20days%20and%20require%20a%20(free)%20rewards%20membership%20to%20claim%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20I%20hadn't%20gotten%20lucky%20with%20the%20deals%20running%20that%20week%2C%20or%20if%20I%20didn't%20have%20a%20Kroger%20card%2C%20I%20could%20have%20easily%20shelled%20out%20about%20%2430%20or%20more%20for%20the%20same%20cart.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20Kroger%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fdeals%2Fprime-day-editor-shopping-hacks-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAmazon's%20prices%20change%20often%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20for%20better%20or%20for%20worse.%20I%20could%20see%20exactly%20how%20much%20by%20using%20the%20%26quot%3Bprice%20history%26quot%3B%20feature.%20For%20example%2C%20the%2012-pack%20of%20Coca-Cola%20alone%20ranged%20in%20price%20from%20%246.29%20to%20%248.89%20over%20the%20past%2030%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrice-wise%2C%20Amazon%20was%20out%20of%20the%20running%20for%20me%20early%20on%20as%20my%20cart%20passed%20%2470.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20bright%20side%2C%20the%20higher%20price%20came%20with%20the%20most%20convenience%3A%20I%20wouldn't%20have%20to%20drive%20anywhere%20or%20pay%20for%20delivery%2C%20given%20that%20I'm%20already%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Famazon-prime-benefits%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPrime%20member%3C%2Fa%3E.%20(The%20membership%20costs%20about%20%24139%20a%20year%20and%20comes%20with%20other%20perks.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMy%20Walmart%20haul%20came%20out%20the%20least%20expensive%20overall%2C%20but%20Kroger%20was%20very%20close%20behind.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224896%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Woman%20smilin%20with%20cart%20in%20Walmart%20aisle%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4e7fe6d3a449ec3445f528%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223672%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESavannah%20Born%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20Walmart%20cart%2C%20complete%20with%20all%20nine%20categories%20of%20items%2C%20came%20to%20%2452.32.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20attempt%20to%20match%20the%20Walmart%20quantities%20as%20closely%20as%20possible%2C%20my%20Kroger%20cart%20%E2%80%94%20using%20my%20card%20and%20the%20deals%20available%20at%20the%20time%20%E2%80%94came%20to%20%2458.52.%20I%20had%20150%20plates%20instead%20of%20200%2C%20though%2C%20and%20an%20extra%20dozen%20cans%20of%20soda%20(given%20I%20wanted%2048%20cans%20but%20got%20three%2012-packs%20free%20with%20my%20purchase%20of%20two).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESure%2C%20this%20isn't%20a%20perfect%20science%2C%20but%20the%20closeness%20of%20the%20totals%20made%20Walmart's%20price%20reductions%20feel%20a%20little%20less%20impressive%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20since%20Walmart%20had%20a%20slight%20advantage%20in%20dictating%20which%20items%20I%20compared.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EFor%20reliably%20low%20prices%2C%20I'd%20go%20back%20to%20Walmart%20%E2%80%94%20but%20I'm%20keeping%20a%20close%20eye%20on%20Kroger's%20rotating%20deals.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224896%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Woman%20smiling%20in%20front%20of%20Walmart%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4e8b9db3a8c16f7e8ec