caption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EOpenAI's%20new%20GPT-Live%20model%20promises%20more%20natural%20human-to-AI%20conversations.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20will%20add%20%26quot%3Bmmhm%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bsure%26quot%3B%20while%20the%20user%20talks%20%E2%80%94%20and%20nixes%20its%20signature%20pregnant%20pauses.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20update%20is%20part%20of%20a%20trend.%20AI%20labs%20are%20trying%20to%20make%20conversations%20feel%20less%20like%20passing%20batons.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20wants%20ChatGPT%20to%20stop%20waiting%20for%20its%20turn.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20a%20Wednesday%20livestream%2C%20the%20company%20unveiled%20GPT-Live%2C%20a%20new%20voice%20model%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-chatgpt-advanced-voice-mode-heres-what-to-expect-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epowering%20ChatGPT%20Voice%3C%2Fa%3E.%20OpenAI%20says%20the%20update%20is%20built%20to%20make%20talking%20with%20AI%20feel%20more%20like%20talking%20to%20a%20human.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20waiting%20for%20a%20clean%20pause%20at%20the%20end%20of%20every%20sentence%20before%20responding%2C%20for%20example%2C%20the%20assistant%20can%20listen%20and%20speak%20simultaneously%2C%20OpenAI%20says.%20It%20will%20also%20acknowledge%20the%20user%20with%20an%20intermittent%20%26quot%3Bmmhm%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3Byeah%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bgot%20it%26quot%3B%20while%20the%20human%20is%20still%20talking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20one%20demo%2C%20a%20user%20asked%20ChatGPT%20to%20fact-check%20the%20date%20of%20a%20coming%20meeting%20while%20also%20checking%20the%20weather%20and%20traffic%20along%20their%20route.%20ChatGPT%20responded%20with%20short%20acknowledgments%20like%20%26quot%3Bhmm%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bsure%2C%26quot%3B%20then%20continued%20working%20through%20the%20request%20without%20losing%20the%20thread%20as%20the%20user%20added%20more%20information%20requests.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20also%20showed%20off%20ChatGPT's%20ability%20to%20translate%20language%20in%20real%20time.%20Previous%20turn-based%20assistants%20had%20to%20wait%20for%20the%20speaker%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flanguage-translator-uses-ai-wont-replace-adapt-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efinish%20before%20translating%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Now%2C%20a%20full-duplex%20assistant%20%E2%80%94%20one%20that%20can%20listen%20and%20talk%20at%20the%20same%20time%20%E2%80%94%20can%20keep%20pace%20more%20naturally%20as%20a%20conversation%20unfolds%2C%20the%20company%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGreg%20Brockman%2C%20OpenAI's%20president%2C%20described%20the%20update%20during%20the%20livestream%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bmuch%20more%20natural%20way%20of%20interacting%20with%20your%20computer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20is%20not%20the%20only%20company%20trying%20to%20make%20AI%20voice%20assistants%20feel%20less%20like%20a%20baton-passing%20chatbot%20and%20more%20like%20an%20active%20listener.%20In%20May%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthinking-machines-lab-key-talent-meta-openai-xai-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EThinking%20Machines%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20AI%20lab%20led%20by%20former%20OpenAI%20chief%20technology%20officer%20Mira%20Murati%2C%20teased%20similar%20technology.%20The%20company%20said%20its%20interaction%20models%20are%20designed%20to%20handle%20input%20and%20output%20continuously%20across%20audio%2C%20video%2C%20and%20text%2C%20instead%20of%20relying%20on%20the%20stop-and-start%20rhythm%20of%20traditional%20chatbots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThinking%20Machines%20said%20the%20updated%20models%20can%20%26quot%3Bhandle%20interaction%20natively%26quot%3B%20and%20smooth%20out%20human-to-AI%20interactions%20%26quot%3Brather%20than%20forcing%20humans%20to%20contort%20themselves%20to%20AI%20interfaces.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20update%20also%20arrives%20as%20AI%20language%20models%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fc