%20on%20streaming%20platforms%2C%20they%20might%20wonder%20how%20Jake%20Johnson%20never%20received%20an%20Emmy%20nom%20for%20his%20role.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Actor%20Jake%20Johnson%20attends%20the%20world%20premiere%20of%20Sony%20Pictures%20Animation%20and%20Marvel's%20%26quot%3BSpider-Man%3A%20Into%20The%20Spider-Verse%26quot%3B%20at%20The%20Regency%20Village%20Theatre%20on%20December%2001%2C%202018%20in%20Westwood%2C%20California.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4e5766965805a2c542e121%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222100%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJake%20Johnson.%3Cp%3EPaul%20Archuleta%2FFilmMagic%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNew%20Girl%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20was%20then%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-short-form-video-licensing-deal-partnership-video-podcasts-youtube-2026-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENetflix%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20got%20a%20serious%20bump%20in%20viewership%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20as%20stressed%20people%20looked%20for%20something%20sweet%20and%20gut-bustingly%20funny%20to%20watch.%20It's%20now%20available%20on%20Peacock%20and%20Hulu.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20while%20Max%20Greenfield%20and%20Zooey%20Deschanel%20were%20deservedly%20recognized%20by%20the%20Television%20Academy%20for%20their%20performances%20as%20Schmidt%20and%20Jessica%20Day%2C%20respectively%2C%20and%20Lamorne%20Morris%20was%20finally%20recognized%20for%20%26quot%3BFargo%26quot%3B%20in%202024%2C%20Johnson%20was%20snubbed%20for%20all%20seven%20seasons%20for%20his%20role%20as%20Nick%20Miller.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJohnson%20is%20currently%20starring%20on%20the%20Apple%20TV%2B%20series%20%26quot%3BMaximum%20Pleasure%20Guaranteed%2C%26quot%3B%20so%20a%20golden%20statue%20could%20be%20in%20his%20future%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EEllen%20Pompeo%20has%20been%20the%20heart%20and%20soul%20of%20%26quot%3B