he%20only%20show%20she%20starred%20in.%20Sagal%20played%20Peggy%20Bundy%20on%20%26quot%3BMarried...%20with%20Children%26quot%3B%20for%2011%20seasons%20and%20was%20one%20of%20the%20show's%20most%20iconic%20characters.%20She%20also%20voiced%20Leela%20on%20%26quot%3BFuturama%26quot%3B%20for%20seven%20seasons%20and%20starred%20on%20%26quot%3B8%20Simple%20Rules%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20none%20of%20which%20garnered%20a%20nomination.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20fact%20that%20Wendell%20Pierce%20was%20never%20nominated%20for%20his%20work%20on%20%26quot%3BThe%20Wire%26quot%3B%20seems%20egregious%20to%20us.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221881%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Wendell%20Pierce%20Frederick%20M.%20Brown%20Getty%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5d30c6f836e03c0bab56ed74%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221411%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EFrederick%20M.%20Brown%2FGetty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Wire%26quot%3B%20is%20heralded%20as%20one%20of%20the%20greatest%20shows%20of%20all%20time%2C%20period.%20But%20it%20never%20won%20an%20Emmy%2C%20and%20it%20was%20only%20nominated%20for%20two%20during%20its%20five-season%20run.%20Pierce%20played%20Det.%20William%20%26quot%3BBunk%26quot%3B%20Moreland%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.esquire.com%2Fentertainment%2Ftv%2Fa35609%2Fwire-best-characters-ranking%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewhom%20Esquire%20called%3C%2Fa%3E%20%26quot%3Bthe%20best-written%20character%20in%20the%20best-written%20show%20in%20the%20history%20of%20television.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20all%20of%20his%20co-stars%2C%20he%20didn't%20receive%20an%20Emmy%20nod%20for%20%26quot%3BThe%20Wire.%26quot%3B%20But%20some%20of%20them%20have%20been%20honored%20for%20their%20other%20work%2C%20like%20Idris%20Elba%20for%20%26quot%3BLuther%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20late%20Michael%20K.%20Williams%20for%20%26quot%3BWhen%20They%20See%20Us%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BLovec