%2C%20and%20had%20a%20great%20TV%20marriage%20with%20Kirsten%2C%20played%20by%20Kelly%20Rowan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe's%20also%20had%20stand-out%20guest%20roles%20on%20shows%20like%20%26quot%3BNew%20Girl%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BGrace%20and%20Frankie%26quot%3B%20that%20could%20be%20worthy%20of%20recognition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ECharlie%20Day%2C%20Rob%20Mac%20(n%C3%A9e%20McElhenney)%2C%20and%20Glenn%20Howerton%20have%20never%20been%20nominated%20for%20acting%20once%20in%20the%2017%20seasons%20of%20%26quot%3BIt's%20Always%20Sunny%20in%20Philadelphia.%26quot%3B%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224075%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22rob%20mcelhenney%20charlie%20day%20glenn%20howerton%20in%202016%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F60edb925ca74780018ae9179%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223056%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EActors%20Charlie%20Day%2C%20Rob%20McElhenney%2C%20and%20Glenn%20Howerton%20attend%20the%20premiere%20for%20the%20sixth%20season%20of%20HBO's%20%26quot%3BGame%20Of%20Thrones%26quot%3B%20at%20TCL%20Chinese%20Theatre%20on%20April%2010%2C%202016%20in%20Hollywood%20City.%3Cp%3EJeff%20Kravitz%2FFilmMagic%20for%20HBO%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20Always%20Sunny's%26quot%3B%20lack%20of%20awards%20recognition%20is%20so%20well%20known%20that%20a%20season%20nine%20episode%20called%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscreenrant.com%2Falways-sunny-gang-tries-win-award-meta-injoke%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Gang%20Tries%20Desperately%20to%20Win%20an%20Award%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20remains%20as%20relevant%20in%202026%20as%20it%20was%20in%202013.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20two%20co-stars%20of%20the%20show%2C%20Danny%20DeVito%20and%20Kaitlin%20Olson%2C%20have%20each%20been%20recognized.%20In%20DeVito's%20case%2C%20he%20won%20in%201981%20for%20%26quot%3BTaxi%2C%26quot%3B%20along%20with%20nominations%20in%201979%2C%201982%2C%20and%201983%20for%20the%20same%20role.%20He%20was%20also%20nominated%20in%202004%20for%20his%20guest%20spot%20on%20%26quot%3BFriends.%26quot%3B%20Olson%20received%20a%20nomination%20in%202020%20for%20her%20role%20in%20Quibi%20series%20%26quot%3BFlipped%26quot%3B%20and%20three%20more%20in%202022%2C%202024%2C%20and%202026%20for%20%26quot%3BHacks.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20three%20original%20dudes%20behind%20the%20show%2C%20Mac%2C%20Day%2C%20and%20Howerton%2C%20have%20all%20been%20snubbed%20%E2%80%94%20not%20only%20for%20their%20iconic%20performances%20as%20Mac%2C%20Charlie%2C%20and%20Dennis%2C%20but%20for%20writing%2C%20directing%2C%20and%20producing%20the%20series%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowerton%20starred%20on%20%26quot%3BAP%20Bio%2C%26quot%3B%20for%20which%20he%20was%20not%20nominated%2C%20while%20Mac%20created%2C%20wrote%2C%20and%20starred%20in%20Apple%20TV%2B%20series%20%26quot%3BMythic%20Quest%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20was%20snubbed%20for%20all%20four%20of%20its%20wonderful%20seasons.%20Day%20also%20produced%20%26quot%3BMythic%20Quest.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMac%20is%20currently%20appearing%20on%20the%20FX%20docu-series%20%26quot%3BWelcome%20to%20Wrexham%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20he%20also%20executive-produces%2C%20so%20that%20finally%20earned%20him%20two%20producing%20wins%2C%20but%20he%20still%20hasn't%20been%20recognized%20for%20acting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ETechnically%2C%20Will%20Smith%20was%20nominated%20in%202021%20as%20a%20producer%20for%20%26quot%3BCobra%20Kai%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20he%20was%20never%20nominated%20for%20%26quot%3BThe%20Fresh%20Prince%20of%20Bel-Air.%26quot%3B%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223812%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22will%20smith%202020.JPG%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F61412e8d2db0850019a97c3b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222859%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EHANNIBAL%20HANSCHKE%2FReuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESmith's%20entire%20movie-star%20career%20can%20be%20traced%20back%20to%20how%20charismatic%20he%20was%20across%20all%20148%20episodes%20of%20the%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Fresh%20Prince%26quot%3B%20was%2C%20and%20is%2C%20a%20pop%20culture%20phenomenon%2C%20with%20characters%20like%20Will%2C%20Carlton%2C%20and%20Uncle%20Phil%2C%20remaining%20relevant%20to%20this%20day%20(just%20ask%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgenius.com%2F4476358%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJ.%20Cole%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DKlJd_bI7DVo%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJoyner%20Lucas%3C%2Fa%3E)%20due%20to%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20performances.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20return%20to%20the%20small%20screen%20could%20secure%20his%20E%20for%20a%20potential%20EGOT%20(as%20he%20now%20has%20an%20Oscar%20and%20a%20Grammy).%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ECourteney%20Cox%20has%20also%20never%20been%20nominated%20for%20an%20acting%20Emmy%2C%20despite%20her%20roles%20on%20%26quot%3BFriends%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BCougar%20Town.%26quot%3B%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222429%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Courteney%20Cox%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F631f8f7989d2b3001894b4ea%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221821%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECourteney%20Cox%3Cp%3EAlex%20J.%20Berliner%2FABImages%20via%20AP%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20downright%20rude%20turn%20of%20events%2C%20Cox%20is%20the%20only%20member%20of%20the%20six-person%20%26quot%3BFriends%26quot%3B%20ensemble%20who%20wasn't%20nominated%20for%20an%20Emmy%20in%20its%2010%20seasons%3A%20Jennifer%20Aniston%20has%20one%20win%20from%20five%20nominations%3B%20Lisa%20Kudrow%20has%20one%20win%20from%20six%20nominations%3B%20Matthew%20Perry%20was%20nominated%20once%3B%20Matt%20LeBlanc%20was%20nominated%20three%20times%3B%20and%20David%20Schwimmer%20was%20nominated%20once.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKudrow%2C%20Aniston%2C%20Perry%2C%20and%20Schwimmer%20were%20all%20nominated%20for%20projects%20%3Cem%3Eoutside%20%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3BFriends%26quot%3B%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECox%20went%20on%20to%20star%20in%20%26quot%3BCougar%20Town%26quot%3B%20for%20six%20seasons%2C%20also%20without%20any%20Emmy%20recognition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20nominated%20for%20a%20Daytime%20Emmy%20for%20producing%20%26quot%3BCelebrity%20Name%20Game%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20received%20a%20nomination%20along%20with%20her%20%26quot%3BFriends%26quot%3B%20co-stars%20for%20producing%20the%20HBO%20Max%20reunion%2C%20but%20Cox%20still%20doesn't%20have%20an%20acting%20nom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EChances%20are%2C%20if%20you've%20watched%20a%20sitcom%20in%20the%20last%2015%20years%2C%20you've%20laughed%20at%20Jason%20Mantzoukas.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jason%20Mantzoukas%20attends%20the%20Netflix's%20%26quot%3BBig%20Mouth%26quot%3B%20Season%208%20Premiere%20(The%20Final%20Season)%20at%20The%20Egyptian%20Theatre%20Hollywood%20on%20May%2022%2C%202025%20in%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20California.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4e5e59d3b3e45765196856%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJason%20Mantzoukas.%3Cp%3EMatt%20Winkelmeyer%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20a%20list%20of%20just%20some%20of%20the%20shows%20Mantzoukas%20has%20been%20in%20since%202011%3A%20%26quot%3BParks%20and%20Recreation%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BModern%20Family%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BBroad%20City%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BTransparent%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BCommunity%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BBrooklyn%20Nine-Nine%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BThe%20Good%20Place%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BDickinson%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BPercy%20Jackson%20and%20the%20Olympians%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BA%20Man%20on%20the%20Inside.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou're%20telling%20me%20that%20not%20one%20of%20those%20hilarious%20supporting%20roles%2C%20guest%20roles%2C%20or%20even%20glorified%20cameos%20was%20worthy%20of%20an%20Emmy%20nom%3F%20Adrian%20Pimento%2C%20Dennis%20Feinstein%2C%20and%20Derek%20were%20all%20iconic%20characters%20and%20deserve%20some%20recognition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20that's%20leaving%20out%20his%20voice%20work%2C%20which%20is%20also%20award-worthy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftv-stars-never-nominated-for-an-emmy-award%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1783528530000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4e73d6d3b3e45765196937%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftv-stars-never-nominated-for-an-emmy-award%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20nominees%20for%20the%2078th%20Emmy%20Awards%20were%20announced%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20and%20these%20TV%20stars%20were%20snubbed%20yet%20again.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Gabbi%20Shaw)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trump%20says%20the%20Iran%20ceasefire%20is%20finished.%20Both%20sides%20have%20been%20trading%20fire%20throughout.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20US%20High%20Mobility%20Artillery%20Rocket%20System%20fires%20at%20night.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4e6282b3a8c16f7e8ec6b5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDespite%20an%20ongoing%20ceasefire%20as%20the%20US%20and%20Iran%20attempted%20to%20broker%20a%20deal%2C%20both%20sides%20have%20kept%20up%20military%20strikes.%3Cp%3EUS%20Army%20Photo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ETrump%20said%20the%20US-Iran%20ceasefire%20is%20over%20and%20threatened%20more%20strikes.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EExchanges%20of%20fire%20have%20been%20ongoing%20throughout%20the%20ceasefire%20and%20negotiations.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMost%20recently%2C%20Iran%20attacked%20commercial%20vessels%20in%20the%20Strait%20of%20Hormuz.%20The%20US%20then%20struck%20over%2080%20Iranian%20targets.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump%20said%20Wednesday%20he%20thinks%20the%20Iran%20ceasefire%20is%20%26quot%3Bover.%26quot%3B%20Throughout%20it%2C%20there's%20been%20a%20lot%20of%20shooting%2C%20and%20more%20strikes%20may%20be%20on%20the%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20violence%20was%20not%20constant%2C%20but%20it%20never%20fully%20disappeared.%20During%20what%20was%20supposed%20to%20be%20a%20pause%20in%20the%20fighting%20while%20a%20deal%20was%20made%2C%20Iran%20attacked%20US%20forces%2C%20Gulf%20states%2C%20and%20commercial%20shipping%2C%20and%20the%20US%20military%20responded%20with%20its%20own%20strikes%20while%2C%20for%20a%20period%2C%20also%20executing%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-navy-destroyers-are-at-center-of-blockade-squeezing-iran-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eblockade%20of%20Iranian%20ports%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20a%20news%20conference%20at%20the%20NATO%20summit%20in%20Turkey%2C%20Trump%20expressed%20frustration%20with%20Iran%20and%20threatened%20further%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-war-with-iran-by-numbers-energy-drinks-to-targets-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emilitary%20action%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20want%20to%20deal%20with%20them%20anymore%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAs%20far%20as%20I'm%20concerned%2C%20it's%20over.%26quot%3B%20Trump%20added%20that%20the%20US%20will%20%26quot%3Bvery%20probably%26quot%3B%20attack%20Iran%20on%20Wednesday%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foil-wti-brent-crude-price-us-iran-war-trump-ceasefire-2026-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EOil%20prices%20surged%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20news%20after%20having%20earlier%20returned%20to%20pre-war%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20night%20before%20the%20president's%20decision%2C%20the%20US%20said%20it%20conducted%20a%20%26quot%3Bseries%20of%20powerful%20strikes%26quot%3B%20against%20Iran%20in%20retaliation%20for%20Tehran%20attacking%20three%20commercial%20vessels%20in%20the%20Strait%20of%20Hormuz%20on%20Tuesday.%20US%20Central%20Command%20said%20American%20forces%20hit%20more%20than%2080%20Iranian%20targets%2C%20including%20air%20defense%20systems%2C%20command%20and%20control%20networks%2C%20and%20anti-ship%20missiles%20around%20the%20strait.%20They%20also%20struck%20over%2060%20Iranian%20Revolutionary%20Guard%20small%20boats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20strikes%2C%20CENTCOM%20said%2C%20were%20meant%20%26quot%3Bto%20impose%20heavy%20costs%20for%20targeting%20and%20attacking%20commercial%20shipping%20crewed%20by%20innocent%20civilians%20in%20an%20international%20waterway.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20added%20that%20Iran's%20attacks%20on%20civilian%20shipping%20were%20a%20violation%20of%20the%20US-Iran%20ceasefire.%20Trump%20expressed%20a%20similar%20sentiment%20at%20the%20NATO%20summit%2C%20accusing%20Iran%20of%20violating%20the%20agreement%20%26quot%3Bevery%20day.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20and%20Iran%20agreed%20to%20a%20two-week%20ceasefire%20in%20early%20April.%20Since%20then%2C%20the%20truce%20has%20been%20less%20of%20a%20ceasefire%20and%20more%20of%20a%20managed%20low-intensity%20conflict%20that%20has%20repeatedly%20threatened%20to%20escalate.%20Operation%20Epic%20Fury%20concluded%2C%20but%20the%20US%20military%20has%20remained%20active.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225472%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20large%20Iranian-flagged%20cargo%20vessel%20sails%20in%20blue%20water.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4e62f6d3b3e4576519687a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223648%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUS%20forces%20interdicted%20and%20disabled%20over%20a%20hundred%20Iranian-flagged%20vessels%20as%20part%20of%20a%20blockade%20on%20Iranian%20ports.%3Cp%3EUS%20Marine%20Corps%20Photo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20ceasefire%20went%20into%20effect%2C%20the%20US%20Navy%20said%20it%20was%20clearing%20mines%20in%20the%20Strait%20of%20Hormuz%20and%20had%20established%20a%20blockade%20of%20Iranian%20ports.%20Over%20the%20following%20weeks%2C%20the%20US%20military%20used%20force%20to%20disable%20multiple%20Iranian-flagged%20vessels%20accused%20of%20running%20the%20blockade.%20These%20blockade-related%20engagements%20involved%20the%20use%20of%20guns%2C%20precision%20munitions%2C%20and%20Hellfire%20missiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20early%20May%2C%20Iran%20launched%20missiles%2C%20drones%2C%20and%20small%20boats%20at%20US%20destroyers%20in%20the%20strait.%20US%20forces%20responded%20by%20destroying%20the%20threats%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-forces-middle-east-need-more-bunker-buster-bombs-cooper-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elaunching%20strikes%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20launch%20sites%2C%20command-and-control%20centers%2C%20and%20reconnaissance%20nodes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToward%20the%20end%20of%20May%2C%20Iran%20lobbed%20missiles%20at%20US%20Gulf%20state%20allies%2C%20sent%20attack%20drones%20into%20the%20Strait%20of%20Hormuz%2C%20and%20also%20downed%20an%20American%20MQ-1%20Predator%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Edrone%20the%20US%20said%20was%20operating%20in%20international%20airspace.%20Central%20Command%20said%20US%20fighter%20aircraft%20responded%20to%20the%20latter%20incident%20by%20knocking%20out%20Iranian%20air%20defenses%2C%20a%20ground%20control%20station%2C%20and%20one-way%20attack%20drones%20that%20posed%20a%20threat%20to%20ships%20sailing%20in%20regional%20waters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIncidents%20such%20as%20these%20continued%20on%20into%20June%2C%20with%20Iran%20launching%20missiles%20and%20drones%20toward%20US%20forces%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20international%20commercial%20shipping%20vessels%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-iran-switzerland-talks-called-off-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EStrait%20of%20Hormuz%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20US-allied%20Gulf%20states.%20CENTCOM%20continually%20responded%2C%20intercepting%20the%20threats%20and%20striking%20Iranian%20facilities.%20Military%20action%20was%20characterized%20as%20defensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225790%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20AH-64E%20Apache%20assigned%20to%20the%2082nd%20Airborne%20Division%2C%20prepares%20to%20land%20in%20a%20forward%20arming%20and%20refueling%20point%20in%20order%20to%20receive%20refuel%20before%20conducting%20operations%20for%20Operation%20Epic%20Fury%20in%20the%20US%20Central%20Command%20area%20of%20responsibility%2C%20May%202%2C%202026.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a27f54aea70485acd8b16cb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223860%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20US%20launched%20retaliatory%20strikes%20on%20Iran%20after%20the%20downing%20of%20an%20Apache%20in%20June.%3Cp%3EUS%20Marine%20Corps%20photo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20early%20June%2C%20CENTCOM%20said%20that%20American%20forces%20had%20rescued%20the%20crew%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-navy-surface-drone-rescued-american-soldiers-after-apache-crashed-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUS%20AH-64%20Apache%20helicopter%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20it%20went%20down%20while%20patrolling%20regional%20waters.%20Later%2C%20Trump%20said%20Iran%20shot%20down%20an%20Apache%20while%20it%20was%20patrolling%20near%20the%20Strait%20of%20Hormuz%20and%20vowed%20US%20retaliation.%20In%20response%2C%20the%20US%20again%20struck%20Iranian%20targets%2C%20specifically%20air%20defenses%2C%20ground-control%20stations%2C%20and%20a%20surveillance%20radar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20day%20later%2C%20more%20US%20combat%20assets%20hammered%20surveillance%2C%20communications%2C%20and%20air%20defense%20targets%20across%20Iran.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20the%20month%2C%20Trump%20had%20noted%20the%20exchanges%20of%20fire%20happening%20during%20the%20ceasefire.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20different%20part%20of%20the%20world%2C%20you%20know%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI'd%20say%20in%20that%20part%2C%20a%20ceasefire%20is%20when%20you're%20shooting%20in%20a%20more%20moderate%20manner.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETensions%20between%20the%20US%20and%20Iran%20eased%20briefly%20with%20a%20mid-June%20memorandum%20of%20understanding%2C%20the%20conclusion%20of%20the%20US%20blockade%2C%20and%20a%20promise%20by%20Iran%20to%20again%20open%20the%20Strait%20of%20Hormuz.%20Disagreements%20over%20interpretation%20of%20the%20document%2C%20however%2C%20led%20to%20more%20violent%20engagements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20late%20June%2C%20Iran%20launched%20multiple%20attacks%20on%20commercial%20shipping%2C%20leading%20the%20US%20to%20respond%20with%20retaliatory%20strikes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThrough%20the%20ups%20and%20downs%2C%20Trump%20has%20repeatedly%20said%20he%20believes%20Iran%20wants%20to%20make%20a%20deal%2C%20but%20at%20the%20NATO%20summit%20this%20week%2C%20Trump%20said%20that%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Ba%20waste%20of%20time%26quot%3B%20dealing%20with%20the%20Iranian%20side%20and%20questioned%20whether%20a%20deal%20could%20be%20reached.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20has%20maintained%20that%20its%20primary%20goal%20in%20its%20negotiations%20with%20Iran%20is%20to%20ensure%20Tehran%20cannot%20build%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbombings-set-back-iran-nuclear-program-likely-didnt-kill-it-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Enuclear%20weapon%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20will%20never%20build%20a%20nuclear%20weapon%20under%20our%20deal%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20know%20if%20we're%20going%20to%20have%20a%20deal%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said%20at%20the%20summit%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3Bwe%20may%20just%20do%20it%20without%20a%20deal%20because%20you%20know%20what%2C%20it's%20easier.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-iran-ceasefire-is-over-shooting-didnt-fully-stop-2026-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1783528435000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4e658ed3a449ec3445f418%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-iran-ceasefire-is-over-shooting-didnt-fully-stop-2026-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Fighting%20only%20slowed.%20Throughout%20the%20ceasefire%2C%20Iran%20attacked%20commercial%20vessels%2C%20US%20forces%2C%20and%20Gulf%20states%2C%20and%20the%20US%20responded%20with%20force.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22cpanella%40businessinsider.com%20(Chris%20Panella)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A95%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Scientists%20in%20Singapore%20have%20found%20a%20way%20to%20transform%20shrimp%20shell%20waste%20into%20'carbon-negative'%20hydrogen%20fuel%2C%20turning%20biomass%20waste%20into%20valuable%20climate%20solutions%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1783528043000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-132267921%2Cimgsize-114252.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fscience%2Fscientists-in-singapore-have-found-a-way-to-transform-shrimp-shell-waste-into-carbon-negative-hydrogen-fuel-turning-biomass-waste-into-valuable-climate-solutions%2Farticleshow%2F132267304.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F132267304.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EResearchers%20have%20pioneered%20a%20groundbreaking%20method%20that%20transforms%20organic%20waste%20into%20hydrogen%20fuel%2C%20while%20simultaneously%20generating%20protein%20suitable%20for%20aquaculture%20feed%20and%20calcium%20carbonate.%