ing%20classic%20with%20lace%2C%20your%20sister%20who%20got%20married%20five%20years%20ago%20wants%20you%20to%20repurpose%20her%20dress%20and%20wear%20it%20%E2%80%94%20the%20pressure%20to%20indulge%20these%20opinions%20can%20be%20weighty%2C%20especially%20when%20they%20come%20from%20such%20important%20people%20in%20your%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20from%20experience%2C%20the%20difference%20between%20seeing%20someone%20in%20a%20dress%20they%20felt%20forced%20or%20pressured%20to%20get%20versus%20seeing%20a%20bride%20wearing%20a%20gown%20that%20truly%20makes%20them%20happy%20is%20incredibly%20palpable.%20Wear%20what%20brings%20you%20joy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22294039e2-edcb-4bf5-bdd2-98650df98883%5C%22%3EStill%20shopping%20for%20a%20dress%20after%20you've%20purchased%20your%20gown%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225221%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20looking%20through%20a%20rack%20of%20wedding%20gowns.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4e7132b3a8c16f7e8ec75d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223481%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMany%20brides%20continue%20looking%20at%20dresses%20after%20purchasing.%3Cp%3EMint%20Images%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20temptation%20to%20continue%20looking%20at%20wedding%20gowns%20after%20you've%20said%20yes%20to%20your%20dress%20is%20real.%20There%20are%20so%20many%20pretty%20dresses%20and%20a%20lot%20of%20wedding-inspiration%20Instagram%20accounts%20and%20Pinterest%20boards.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlus%2C%20it's%20not%20uncommon%20to%20wonder%20if%20there%20may%20be%20an%20ensemble%20that's%20more%20perfect%20than%20the%20one%20you%20bought.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20this%20is%20the%20root%20of%20your%20regret%20%E2%80%94%20feeling%20like%20there%20are%20so%20many%20other%20options%20out%20there%20%E2%80%94%20the%20best%20advice%20is%20to%20honor%20the%20choice%20you%20made.%20There%20will%20always%20be%20gorgeous%20gowns%2C%20but%20only%20one%20is%20your%20wedding%20dress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223934f467-9763-4546-941e-ad0d255e5679%5C%22%3EHyperfocusing%20on%20one%20part%20of%20the%20gown%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226863%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20holding%20the%20strap%20on%20a%20wedding%20gown.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4e6c99d3b3e457651968f0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225147%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EYou%20can%20always%20call%20the%20store%20and%20ask%20to%20try%20on%20your%20dress%20again.%3Cp%3Emadisonwi%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPicture%20this%3A%20You%20get%20home%20from%20the%20bridal%20salon%20after%20purchasing%20your%20dress%20and%20start%20reviewing%20your%20photos%20from%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20zooming%20in%20on%20a%20certain%20feature%20of%20the%20gown%20%E2%80%94%20whether%20it%20be%20a%20mesh%20V-neck%2C%20the%20color%20of%20the%20lace%2C%20or%20the%20presence%20or%20absence%20of%20sleeves%20%E2%80%94%20you%20fixate%20on%20it.%20In%20a%20moment%2C%20this%20makes%20you%20question%20the%20entire%20purchase.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWedding%20gowns%20aren't%20something%20we%20purchase%20every%20day%2C%20so%20it's%20normal%20to%20fixate%20on%20details%20like%20a%20super-long%20train%20or%20a%20heavily%20beaded%20bodice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20my%20experience%2C%20the%20best%20solution%20is%20to%20call%20the%20store%20and%20ask%20to%20try%20the%20dress%20on%20again.%20This%20will%20help%20you%20to%20determine%20whether%20you%20still%20love%20the%20gown%20as%20much%20as%20you%20did%20when%20you%20bought%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20still%20hesitant%20about%20certain%20aspects%20of%20your%20gown%2C%20talk%20to%20your%20bridal%20consultant%20about%20it%2C%20as%20they%20may%20be%20able%20to%20walk%20you%20through%20other%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222c4480f6-8075-4752-9866-7c9a425d8e98%5C%22%3ERegretting%20spending%20so%20much%20money%20on%20a%20dress%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure