boosting%20lowering%20barriers%20for%20small%20businesses%20across%20different%20sectors%20and%20fueling%20a%20new%20wave%20of%20entrepreneurship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20effect%2C%20AI%20allows%20businesses%20to%20access%20scale%20economics%20before%20they%20have%20fully%20scaled%2C%20pooling%20capabilities%20across%20functions%20and%20lowering%20the%20output%20threshold%20at%20which%20expansion%20becomes%20economic%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20macro%20strategist%20Frank%20Flight.%20%26quot%3BNever%20bet%20against%20America.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEconomists%20such%20as%20Mohamed%20El-Erian%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-returns-us-economic-outlook-american-exceptionalism-el-erian-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehave%20stated%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20American%20exceptionalism%20is%20facing%20significant%20challenges%20as%20market%20headwinds%20shift%20while%20others%20have%20suggested%20that%20the%20US%20has%20already%20started%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-outlook-us-vs-international-stocks-american-exceptionalism-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elosing%20its%20edge%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20other%20leading%20economies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Citadel%20Securities%20maintains%20that%20on%20the%20contrary%2C%20AI%20is%20already%20helping%20the%20US%20keep%20its%20place%20as%20a%20global%20economic%20superpower%20by%20giving%20rise%20to%20a%20booming%20entrepreneurial%20economy%20marked%20by%20hustle%20culture%20and%20innovation.%20As%20Flight%20noted%2C%20the%20US'%20small-business%20sector%20generates%20almost%2040%25%20of%20economic%20output.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAI%20may%20pay%20its%20greatest%20dividend%20by%20compounding%20America's%20hustle%20culture%3A%20Lowering%20the%20cost%20of%20business%20formation%2C%20increasing%20founder%20leverage%2C%20and%20turning%20the%20country's%20instinct%20for%20innovation%20into%20new%20economic%20activity%2C%26quot%3B%20Flight%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMuch%20of%20the%20recent%20discussion%20of%20AI%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-resilience-after-broadcom-avgo-earnings-ai-trade-winners-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehas%20centered%3C%2Fa%3E%20around%20the%20stock%20market%20and%20the%20staggering%20buildout%20of%20infrastructure%20like%20data%20centers.%20But%20Flight%20added%20that%20it%20may%20be%20time%20for%20a%20new%20conversation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThus%20far%2C%20the%20AI%20theme%20has%20been%20framed%20around%20frontier%20labs%2C%20hyperscalers%2C%20and%20bottlenecks%20in%20compute%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20think%20an%20equally%20powerful%20focus%20is%20what%20AI%20does%20for%20the%20builders%2C%20founders%2C%20and%20small%20businesses%20that%20drive%20such%20a%20large%20share%20of%20the%20economy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESmall%20businesses%20have%20historically%20struggled%20with%20limited%20staffing%20and%20resources%2C%20particularly%20outside%20of%20major%20metro%20areas.%20Now%2C%20as%20Flight%20notes%2C%20AI%20is%20enabling%20business%20owners%20to%20access%20economies%20of%20scale%20and%20expand%20in%20ways%20that%20allow%20them%20to%20compete%20with%20larger%20peers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20acknowledged%20this%20may%20mean%20AI%20automating%20away%20certain%20tasks.%20But%20while%20that%20may%20result%20in%20job%20loss%2C%20Flight%20added%20that%20it%20is%20also%20likely%20to%20create%20new%20business%20opportunities%20that%20ultimately%20create%20more%20jobs%20as%20businesses%20grow%20and%20explore%20new%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20illustrate%20this%2C%20he%20cited%20the%20example%20of%20Jevons%20Paradox%2C%20an%20economic%20principle%20that%20maintains%20that%20an%20innovative%20new%20technology%20creates%20more%20efficiency%2C%20it%20ultimately%20leads%20to%20more%20jobs%20being%20created.%20Apollo%20chief%20economist%20Torsten%20Sl%C3%B8k%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-job-market-labor-unemployment-jevons-paradox-apollo-torsten-slok-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erecently%20made%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20same%20argument%2C%20predicting%20that%20AI%20would%20lead%20to%20a%20labor-market%20boom%2C%20rather%20than%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoldman-sachs-economist-predicts-ai-displacing-15-million-jobs-2026-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejobs%20wipeout%3C%2Fa%3E%20many%20have%20feared.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-small-business-hustle-culture-citadel-securities-economy-labor-market-2026-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1783525215000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4e639bd3a449ec3445f3eb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-small-business-hustle-culture-citadel-securities-economy-labor-market-2026-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Citadel%20Securities%20says%20AI%20is%20bolstering%20one%20of%20America's%20biggest%20economic%20advantages%2C%20lowering%20barriers%20for%20side%20hustlers%20and%20entrepreneurs.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22sobrient%40insider.com%20(Samuel%20O'Brient)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bowen%3A%20For%20all%20his%20bluster%2C%20Trump%20has%20no%20better%20option%20than%20talks%20with%20Iran%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1783524600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Face%2Fbranded_news%2F1200%2Fcpsprodpb%2F7fa2%2Flive%2F54d324f0-7ae1-11f1-9a9c-53fd8f110370.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcy8we3j14ndo%232%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20negotiating%20process%20is%20fragile%20and%20recent%20US%20strikes%20show%20how%20hard%20it%20will%20be%20to%20reach%20agreement%2C%20writes%20BBC's%20Internati